    <x:String x:Key="TxtFakenvapiTip">Required for AMD/Intel GPUs to enable DLSS FG with Nukem mod</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtNukemTip">Nukem's DLSSG-to-FSR3 mod for Frame Generation</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtFakenvapiHelpTip">Tricks the game into detecting an NVIDIA graphics card, allowing you to bypass hardware restrictions and enable DLSS technologies on AMD or Intel GPUs.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtNukemHelpTip">A mod by Nukem that replaces native DLSS Frame Generation with AMD FSR 3 Frame Generation, enabling frame generation on any compatible GPU.</x:String>

